# m3_mass_driver.shot — Heavy chassis with a Mass Driver lobs a rocket
# at the dummy. We expect:
#   - One projectile in flight on tick ~5 after fire press
#   - Explosion VFX on impact (sparks fan-out + smoke + screen shake)
#   - AOE damage to the dummy (one rocket should kill via 220 base + AOE)
#   - Multiple limbs detach due to GIB-class hit (mask >= 0x06)
# Bink/self-bink shouldn't matter much for a single shot, but we log it.

window 1280 720
seed   1 1
out    build/shots/m3_mass_driver
loadout Heavy "Mass Driver" - Heavy Standard
contact_sheet sheet cols 4 cell 480 270

# Park player on the dummy platform at the same height as in m1_dummy_kill.
spawn_at 2240 984
mouse    1100 360

at  10 shot t010_idle
at  30 press fire
at  35 release fire           # Mass driver fires at most once per 1100 ms
at  40 shot t040_inflight
at  50 shot t050_inflight
at  60 shot t060_impact
at  80 shot t080_aftermath
at 110 shot t110_aftermath

# Give it time for ragdoll to settle.
burst settle from 130 to 240 every 20

at 260 end
